### Get all contacts
GET http://localhost:8080/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get a contact by email
GET http://localhost:8080/contacts/john.doe@example.com
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Create a new contact
POST http://localhost:8080/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstname": "Jane",
  "lastname": "Smith",
  "email": "jane.smith@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "blue",
  "birthday": "1992-07-15"
}

###

### Update a contact
PUT http://localhost:8080/contacts/jane.smith@example.com
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstname": "Jane",
  "lastname": "Smith",
  "email": "jane.smith@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "green",
  "birthday": "1992-07-15"
}

###

### Delete a contact
DELETE http://localhost:8080/contacts/jane.smith@example.com
Content-Type: application/json

